Nodes.Comment: Run in and follow numbers then get out and repair fences/water on drunks.
Kill rats, get Scrap Metal and put in Scrap-Metal Barrels
Loot Documents on the way. They give 5% Heart progress each.
You can turn in Documents here.
Remember to collect Steam Parts, you'll get the opportunity to turn them in later on.
Glide right over the POI to get it. You may want to lose some height but make sure to be able to hit the gap.
Do event if it's up otherwise get an Essence Coagulator and open portals/kill Imps

DetachedNodes.Comment: Interact with this Collection Barrel to turn in the Steam Parts. You can also get Bombs to blow up Dead Steam Creatures from the Heart NPC. Bottom dialog option.
